title: Impeachment, Healthcare & USMCA
itunes:title: Impeachment, Healthcare & USMCA
description:
Kevin spoke with Bloomberg's Senior Executive Editor for Government and Economics Marty Schenker, Kevin Walling, Democratic Strategist at HG Creative Media, and A.B. Stoddard, Associate Editor & Columnist @ Real Clear Politics.


They discussed USMCA, Impeachment, healthcare and the 2020 elections.
